data.description: Discover your dream home located just minutes away from Lockheed Martin! This meticulously maintained 3-bed, 2-bath gem boasts recent foundation work, ensuring lasting stability. With two living areas and a private primary bedroom on the second level, it's perfect for families or those seeking extra space. Embrace convenience with the attached two-car garage, ensuring effortless arrivals. Step into a sprawling, pet-friendly backyard, perfect for outdoor activities, and unwind beneath the covered patio. This home is eligible for the Bank of America Grant Program for assistance with down payments and closing costs to eligible buyers.
